---
title: Strip Steak Over Truffled Mashed Potatoes with Green Beans Amandine
description: When you want to treat yourself to something luxuriantly tasty, nothing offers instant gratification better than a good steak. And we’ve got a great one with our New York strip, which is prized for its marbling and flavor. All it needs to be perfectly sublime is a simple pan sauce and some equally decadent sides, like almond green beans and truffled mashed potatoes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5a149f007901f9316a4a4892-363fbcef.jpg
